b'Fuku-chan no Zousan Butai': b'The second film of the Fuku-chan triology. Based on a popular newspaper comic strip at the time, Fuku-chan was re-invented for propaganda use. In this one Fuku-chan tries to rally up the fighting spirit of the troops.'
[b'Fuku-chan no Sensuikan', b'Fuku-chan no Kishuu', b'Fuku-chan']
